{"tid":469770,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"今日，我踩親四腳蛇條尾","createTime":"2017-11-15T15:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T08:39:48.000Z","uid":119446,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fa69b54994553962b628abb5ecf1c3a08318038a","tid":469770,"uid":119446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:53:08.000Z","msg":"出門口穿拖鞋既時候<br />\n腳板底突然傳出一陣奇異既觸感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻縮腳，同時有隻野極速逃離我隻拖鞋<br />\n行近望，原來係隻四腳爬爬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/234822_ba132a17434a095a59ba3499cbbe0359.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F234822_ba132a17434a095a59ba3499cbbe0359.JPG&h=69347824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我腳底依然有奇異既觸感<br />\n再望一望隻拖鞋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/235000_1adc79028d532bc630f2e1a613c8a24c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F235000_1adc79028d532bc630f2e1a613c8a24c.JPG&h=2192806e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry, 踩親你條尾<br />\n祝你早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff65f1035c8fe1007c13ce62f8a665777076d1b","tid":469770,"uid":139252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5133a4299c31c621ff63ddaba952781702c70f","tid":469770,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0019a849d78d8e2109eacc916dc66812b27642f0","tid":469770,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}